Almost every item was damaged in some way. Most had scuffs running down the mugs. Others came broken or chipped. The print quality is great, they just can't seem to store and/or ship their items well. We have had mugs from 3 other companies and they managed to ship them in good condition every time. They should invest in better shipping packaging. One of the boxes even had someone's beverage bottle trash in it. The phone number on the shipping label is also disconnected so trying to contact them direct to avoid having to leave this review was fruitless. They should probable stick to T-shirts if they aren't versed in how to ship fragile items correctly.
